::'''Yujin:''' Hello, welcome to Cloudbreadth Sleeves. Our shop's interior is undergoing renovation at the moment, and isn't available to customers. How may I help you?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm fine, just browsing.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101003-->
:::'''Yujin:''' Please help yourself then.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you have anything popular you can recommend?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101005-->
:::'''Yujin:''' ...Oh, yes.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502101006-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101006-->
::'''Yujin:''' You look somewhat unfamiliar. I trust that you haven't been on Xianzhou long? Cloudbreadth Sleeves is Xianzhou's most prestigious place of couture. Even General Jing Yuan himself has to respect our tailors.
::'''Yujin:''' Forgive me for being blunt: Cloudbreadth Sleeves may be haute couture, but our prices are justified. All Outworlders who come to Xianzhou order their clothes here. Could I interest you in ordering a few custom-made pieces?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502010101_19-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502010101_19-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Can I try one on first?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101011-->
:::'''Yujin:''' Oh, about that, our shop's haute couture has limited quantities. You have to pay in advance to try them out.
:::'''Yujin:''' And this is a new item, so we don't have any discounts available. Are you fine with this?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll pass. Do you have ordinary ready-made clothes?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101014-->
:::'''Yujin:''' The ready-made ones? The most popular among Outworlders is the "Classic Xianzhou Floral" series. But we're sold out right now.
:::'''Yujin:''' Honestly, mass-produced and ready-made lines are outdated and preferred only by Outworlders. We don't stock many of those, and we won't be re-supplying on short notice.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502101016-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101016-->
::'''Yujin:''' Well, if you aren't looking for haute couture, we're pressed for time to entertain you. Please see yourself out.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_502010101_28-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_502010101_28-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you greet Jing Yuan with this attitude as well?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101018-->
:::'''Yujin:''' Of course not, Jing... ahem, General Jing Yuan is an esteemed guest of our Cloudbreadth Sleeves. It's only natural he be treated as one.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll just go ask my bro Jing Yuan about this.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101020-->
:::'''Yujin:''' Oo-er, wait, you... no, you-you know General Jing Yuan!?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} In this day and age, the service presented here is unacceptable!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101022-->
:::'''Yujin:''' Hold it, hold it. I've been in this business for decades. Everything I say has always been in the customer's best interests.
:::'''Yujin:''' You may think it's a slight to you, but even if General Jing Yuan himself comes to tailor his attire, I would address him similarly.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} All right then, I'll ask him right now.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101025-->
:::'''Yujin:''' Hang on, you, no wait- esteemed customer, you know General Jing Yuan!?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502101026-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502101026-->
::'''Yujin:''' Ooh, please forgive me! You're a friend of General Jing Yuan's! This is all a misunderstanding! I wouldn't let you try ready-made clothes because they're all run-of-the-mill fashion lines. How could they be a match for someone who looks as {{MC|f=gorgeous|m=dashing}} as you! Away with them, I say!
::'''Yujin:''' At Cloudbreadth Sleeves, we arrange for tailors to serve our esteemed guests without fail. We've prepared a small gift for you. Please accept it, and let us put all this behind us.
::'''Yujin:''' If it would please you, how about you leave an address and time, and I shall make an appointment? Don't worry. I've already arranged for express passage for you. How about it? Is there anything else you need?
